{"tid":1551169,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國際貿易部： 港取消派代表參加國防及軍用警備展覽","createTime":"2019-09-08T01:04:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T02:07:46.000Z","uid":68738,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9bc43b94f4595d6accee026078043866b6773ea7","tid":1551169,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T01:04:12.000Z","msg":"英國國際貿易部確認，香港不會派代表參加下周在倫敦舉行的國防及軍用警備展覽（DSEI）。<br />\n<br />\n《衞報》早前報道，英國歐米茄研究基金會（Omega Research Foundation）透過香港示威現場圖片，認出港警驅散示威者時所用的一枚N225式橡膠手擲式催淚彈，是由總部設於英國的「Chemring Group」生產。前外相侯俊偉6月曾表明暫停向香港輸出人群管制裝備，但國際貿易部上月仍邀請香港代表出席DSEI。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，工黨議員福克斯克羅夫特（Vicky Foxcroft）在國會向國際貿易大臣兼貿易委員會主席卓慧思（Elizabeth Truss），詢問香港獲邀出席原因，後來國際貿易部投資副部長斯圖爾特（Graham Stuart）表示已確認香港取消派人參加展覽。<br />\n<br />\n下周二舉行的國防及軍用警備展覽，是全歐最大的同類型展覽，有1,600間參展商和40多個展館，會展示多款安全及人群控制裝備。<br />\n<br />\n另外，港人組織「D4HK」（Democracy for Hong Kong）及「Fight for Freedom. Stand with Hong Kong」計劃當地時間周六聯同反軍火貿易組織（CAAT），於DSEI會場外集會，希望香港警方濫用暴力的情況在國際層面上得到更多關注。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190907/60019029\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190907%2F60019029&d=N8yyMuQB0XA0Wgs8sIkprpS9c5E4FlifGpQIAZCXP1E%3D&h=6b7232dc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190907%2F60019029&h=5cd2ce31\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190907/60019029</a>"},{"pid":"e53aeb0e08cea2b1eb5692cb561502be2133415e","tid":1551169,"uid":54681,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T01:05:53.000Z","msg":"柒出國際 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e9d2563bdd2dce5ee84297a7042967d65048ff9","tid":1551169,"uid":92277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T01:05:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SXvHX95.